@startuml
[*] --> ReceiveVideoSuggestionRequest
ReceiveVideoSuggestionRequest --> IdentifyUser : identify user
IdentifyUser --> GatherVideos : gather videos from different sources (user's profile or preferences, trending videos, similar tags, similar genres, promoted)
GatherVideos --> AddAdditionalDetails : add thumbnails and view counts to suggested videos
AddAdditionalDetails --> SendSuggestedVideos : send suggested videos with additional details
SendSuggestedVideos --> [*]
@enduml
